metadata.name: MEGAMI×MIKOTO＝MEGAMIKOTO
metadata.description:
Satsuki Minato's signboard character "MIKOTO" is now MEGAMI!

She lives in a port town and she loves about ships and the sea.
Also, a lot of people gather around her because of her good personality.
She is loved by many people, whether it's a fisherman, a grandmother in the neighborhood, or children in the city.
MIKOTO, who loves the sea, often goes to the fishing port and stares at the ocean, making her feel good while being blown by the sea breeze.

I would be happy if I could bring her to you through her MEGAMI fan art.
As a MEGAMI fan, she is very pleased to have such an opportunity. Thank you very much.

#megamiathome
